description: The index utilizes certain environmental, social, and governance (“ ESG”) criteria to select from the securities included in the Bloomberg U.S. High Yield Very Liquid Index (the “ Base Index”), which is designed to broadly capture the U.S. dollar-denominated, high yield, fixed-rate corporate bond market. Under normal market conditions, it invests at least 80% of the sum of its net assets and the amount of any borrowings for investment purposes in component securities of the index.
name: Nuveen ESG High Yield Corporate Bond
